These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: orchid, azalea, daffodil, zinnia, amaryllis, tulip, bellflower
 1. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 2. the person who growszinnia is somewhere between the person who growstulip and the person who growsamaryllis##7
 3. the person who growsazalea is somewhere between the person who growstulip and the person who growsorchid##7
 4. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
 5. the person who growsbellflower is not to the left of the person who growstulip##8
 6. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
 8. the person who growstulip is somewhere between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growsbellflower##7
 9. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the right of the person who growszinnia##8
10. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Flower   | amaryllis | orchid | azalea | daffodil | zinnia | tulip | bellflower |

