.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
City: edinburgh, prague, new-york, venice, marseilles, san-francisco, liverpool
 1. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 2. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
 3. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to prague##5
 4. the person traveling to prague is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
 6. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
10. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| City   | venice | prague | san-francisco | liverpool | new-york | edinburgh | marseilles |

