.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, 7up, sprite, fanta, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, coffee
 1. the person drinking fanta is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 2. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 6. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking 7up##7
 8. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
 9. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | fanta | coffee | cola | sprite | 7up |

