 6. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 7. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
10. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
