 5. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing scrabble##2
 6. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 8. the person playing poker is somewhere between the person playing chess and the person playing backgammon##7
 9. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |    3     |   4   |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Game   | backgammon | poker | chess | monopoly | mah-jongg | scrabble | canasta |

